content.text: Now let me read the individual plugin.json files to compare:

input.command:
for plugin in plugins/*/plugin.json; do
  name=$(basename $(dirname "$plugin"))
  version=$(grep -o '"version": "[^"]*"' "$plugin" | head -1 | cut -d'"' -f4)
  echo "$name: $version"
done
